\": \"Sam Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Matildas captain ruptured an anterior cruciate ligament, also known as an ACL, at a training camp over the weekend, her club Chelsea confirmed on Monday morning.\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 356, \"end\": 364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0188170496836449e-23, \"text\": \"Matildas\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\", \"score\": 0.9430036116759827, \"rank\": 0.06044132558800746, \"text\": \"ACL\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q39888\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anterior_cruciate_ligament\"}, {\"begin\": 481, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.6888552878494124, \"rank\": 0.4516837101185567, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was at the Women's Super League leaders' warm weather training in Morocco with Chelsea when she sustained the ACL injury, the second one since 2011.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_League\", \"score\": 0.9999498319063536, \"rank\": 5.0122171988980335e-05, \"text\": \"Super League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q